    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. I want to make sure the post isn't just seen as a niche libertarian rant. How would a critic respond to the idea that regulation is a violation of rights, and how can I effectively counter those critiques to show that the regulatory view is actually the one that's flawed?",
